Texts.Chs: 下载最新的绘世者法典条目！
Texts.Eng: Download the newest Skath codex entries!

Texts.Chs: 叶族人看看看看见了大天线！太太太适合当做长长长长矛了！
Texts.Eng: Floran seesss big antenna! Good for sspearss!

Texts.Chs: 我可以用这个访问绘世者的记录！
Texts.Eng: I can access Skath records using this!

Texts.Chs: 我想知道这东西是干什么的？
Texts.Eng: I wonder what this thing does?

Texts.Chs: 似乎绘世者使用数字化存档来记录他们种族的著作。太遗憾了。
Texts.Eng: It seems the Skath record their species' writings digitally. Such a pity.

Texts.Chs: 绘世者似乎对他们法典条目的访问进行了限制。
Texts.Eng: The Skath seem to restrict the access to their codex entries.

Texts.Chs: 这个终端可以用来获取大量关于我们种族的前沿知识。出于安全原因，只有绘世者族人可以登入这个终端。
Texts.Eng: This terminal can be used to access vast amounts of Vanguard knowledge regarding our race. For security reasons, only the Skath can access these.
Used to download Skath codex entries from Norkumsgath.

Texts.Chs: 使用这个终端可以下载到最新的绘世者法典条目。遗憾的是这个终端只允许绘世者的族人登入。
Texts.Eng: With this terminal you can probably download Skath codex entries. The access seems restricted to anyone except the Skath, unfortunately.
